        "subject": "LU-11127 tests: stop running sanity-flr test 34b",
        "message": "LU-11127 tests: stop running sanity-flr test 34b\n\nsanity-flr test 34b fails frequently when run on a Lustre\nfile system configured with DNE. We need to add test 34b\nto the ALWAYS_EXCEPT list and, thus, stop running it until\na fix for the underlying problem can be found.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial mdtcount=1 mdscount=1 testlist=sanity-flr\nTest-Parameters: mdtcount=2 mdscount=1 testlist=sanity-flr\nSigned-off-by: James Nunez <jnunez@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: I959525657b8252d191f3623322d518aa85e99683\n"
